               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Kiros, መልክዐ፡ ኪሮስ፡; Acts of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus, ገድለ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡, Acts of Abba Kiros, ገድለ፡ ኪሮስ።</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="1v" facs="002"/><title type="incomplete" ref="LIT2860RepCh141"/><note>fragment</note></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="2r" to="58r" facs="003"/><title>Acts of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus, Gädlä Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገድለ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡</foreign></title>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1"><locus from="2r" to="41r" facs="003"/><title type="incomplete" ref="LIT1451GadlaG"/><note>incomplete at the beginning</note></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2"><locus from="41r" to="58r" facs="042"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT3977Taammer"/>
                    <note>Thirteen miracles</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      በስመ: አብ: ወወልድ:<gap reason="omitted"/>ንጽሕፍ: ዜና: ገድሉ: ተአምሪሁ: ነፍሱ: ወሥጋሁ:<gap reason="omitted"/>
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="59r" to="85v" facs="060"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT5134KirosGeneral"/>
